## Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Frontend | React + Next.js (App Router) |
| Backend | Next.js API routes (`/app/api`) — Vercel serverless |
| Database | Supabase (Postgres) |
| AI | Claude API (Anthropic) — structured outputs, not raw chat |
| Deployment | Vercel |

