## Out of Scope

Do not build: calendar integration, mobile app, multi-user features, real-time external ingestion, push notifications.

---

## Engineering Standards

- All Claude outputs must be structured (typed response schema, not raw strings)
- Validate at the AI boundary — never trust raw LLM output directly in the UI
- Seed demo data before the sprint ends — do not rely on live input for the demo
- Deploy to Vercel and smoke-test before submission. "It works locally" is not done.
